text: William W. Wemple, Jr. (c. 1898 - October 14, 1972) was an American lawyer and politician. He served as a member of the New York State Assembly from 1929 to 1930. ==References== Category:1890s births Category:1972 deaths Category:Union College (New York) alumni Category:Albany Law School alumni Category:New York (state) lawyers Category:Members of the New York State Assembly
